### 1) Login
POST http://localhost:5176/api/auth-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2) Crear pedido con customizaciones
POST http://localhost:5176/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": "Mesa 3",
  "customer_name": "Prueba Integracion",
  "items": [
    {
      "id": 101,
      "name": "Pizza de pepperoni",
      "qty": 1,
      "price": 230,
      "notes": "Extras: extra queso | Sin: cebolla | Alergia: lactosa | Nota: sin picante"
    }
  ]
}

### 3) Ver pedidos activos
GET http://localhost:5176/api/orders?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Editar pedido (debe responder 200 si backend ya implementado)
PATCH http://localhost:5176/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": 101,
      "name": "Pizza de pepperoni",
      "qty": 2,
      "price": 230,
      "notes": "Extras: extra queso, champinon | Sin: cebolla | Alergia: lactosa | Nota: corte en 8"
    }
  ]
}

### 5) Validar reflejo en GET
GET http://localhost:5176/api/orders?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
